Americans. Lt. Col. <PERSON> Joe </PERSON> <PERSON> Harvey </PERSON>, leader of the <LOCATION> U.S. </LOCATION> team in <LOCATION> Vietnam </LOCATION>, earlier expressed hope for several joint investigation operations in the coming months. `` We are prepared to provide four teams, if <LOCATION> Vietnam </LOCATION> agrees,'' he said. Of the 2,393 Americans missing, 1,757 are in <LOCATION> Vietnam </LOCATION>, 547 in <LOCATION> Laos </LOCATION>, 83 in <LOCATION> Cambodia </LOCATION> and six in <LOCATION> China </LOCATION>. <LOCATION> U.S. </LOCATION> forces withdrew from <LOCATION> Indochina </LOCATION> in 1973 after the conflict cost 58,000 American lives.
